        <a class="author" href="/id171507541" data-from-id="171507541">Сергей Кичигин</a> <a href="/id245973871" class="reply_to" onclick="return wall.showReply(this, '-100384220_4075', '-100384220_4139', event)" rid="245973871" onmouseover="wall.postTooltip(this, '-100384220_4272', {reply: 1})">ответил Александру</a>
